        Collection<QueryEntity> queryEntities()
        Returns current state of configured QueryEntity. QueryEntity can be changed by executing DDL on SQL tables. Note, CacheConfiguration.getQueryEntities() returns initial definition of QueryEntity.
        Returns:
        Query entities for cache.
